      "role": "user",
      "content": "serotonin syndrome sounds scary but i've never heard of it before. is that like actually common or just something they warn everyone about? if i just take a tiny bit, like maybe half a pill or something, is it really going to be that much of a risk? i just really need to get through these next two weeks without feeling so low.",
